{
  "name": "伊格薇爾伏惡魔志 Demonomicon of Iggwilv",
  "type": "equipment",
  "img": "icons/sundries/books/book-open-purple.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">作為一份關於深淵之無限層級及其居民的宏大論文，</span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>伊格薇爾伏惡魔</em></span><em>志</em><span class=\"SpellE\"><em>Demonomicon</em></span><em> of </em><span class=\"SpellE\"><em>Iggwilv</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">是多元宇宙中最詳細而最為褻瀆的關於惡魔學識的記載。這卷書記載了從亙古到現在關於深淵與惡魔的所有</span><span class=\"GramE\">瀆</span>神之物。惡魔們嘗試過刪減其中的文字，而雖有的部分被從書本<span class=\"GramE\">的脊頁上</span>撕下，但大部分章節仍存，而且較之前更能揭示惡魔的秘密。這書所含之物已非褻瀆二字所能形容。一小片不為人知的，無底深淵本身的碎片被囚禁於字字句句之後，使得無論有多少頁被撕下，也能讓<span class=\"GramE\">書時刻</span>保持著更新，這本書也不僅僅只是想要成為一本參考材料。<br /><em><strong>隨機屬性</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。這件神器具有以下隨機屬性，你可以通過對著<em>《地下城主指南》</em>中的</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>「神器」</em></span> <span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">章節擲</span><span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>以決定它們。</p><ul><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">兩項弱效增益屬性</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">一項強效減益屬性</span></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">一項弱效減益屬性</span></li></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br /><em><strong>法術。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">這本書具有</span>8<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能，且每天黎明時恢復</span>1d8<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發已消耗的充能。當你持握它時，你可以用一個動作隨意施展<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.n9RjfSJ88RfFhO1T]{塔莎狂笑術Tasha』s Hideous Laughter}</em>或消耗</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發或更多的充能施展以下法術（</span>DC20<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">）：<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.Vrzu8xpLMvOvOnx6]{防護法陣Magic Circle}</em>（</span>1<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能），</span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.SWopkvFFxAkCwG7W]{魔魂壺Magic Jar}</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">（</span>3<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能），</span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.XbVBvp0A6Nf7imnf]{異界盟誓Planar Ally}</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">（</span>3<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能），</span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.PmucSbzqmGhwisuE]{異界誓縛Planar Binding}</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">（</span>2<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能），</span><span class=\"GramE\"><em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.VveuAHLNPiAY0yd5]{異界傳送Plane Shift}</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">（僅限深淵層級；</span>3<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能），<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.5wQNcY6579h2jLeA]{邪魔召喚術Summon Fiend}</em>（</span>3<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">發充能；出現於本書）。</span><br /><em><strong>深淵學識。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">你可以在你每次進行辨認關於惡魔的訊息的智力檢定或關於深淵的感知（生存）檢定時查閱惡魔志。若如此做，你的檢定使用雙倍的熟練加值。</span><br /><em><strong>鞭笞邪魔。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">你的魔法會為邪魔帶來痛苦。當你攜帶書，併爲自己所施展的法術對一個邪魔進行傷害擲</span><span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>時，直接取滿值而無須擲<span class=\"GramE\">骰</span>。<br /><em><strong>迷惑。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">當你攜帶著書，每次你施展對邪魔的<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.Vrzu8xpLMvOvOnx6]{防護法陣Magic Circle}</em>或<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.PmucSbzqmGhwisuE]{異界誓縛Planar Binding}</em>時，無論你使用了哪個等級的法術位，都視為以</span>9<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">環施展。此外，邪魔在對抗這些法術的豁免檢定上具有劣勢。</span><br /><em><strong>封印。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">惡魔志的前</span>10<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">頁是空白的。持握這本書時，作為一個動作，你可以選擇一個你可見且被困在<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.Vrzu8xpLMvOvOnx6]{防護法陣Magic Circle}</em>中的邪魔。該邪魔必須以劣勢進行一次</span>DC20<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的魅力豁免，豁免失敗則被困在惡魔志的一張空白頁中。並且會附上受困生物廣為人知的名字與墮落內容的詳細文字。使用后，直到下次黎明前，這項動作不能再次使用。</span><br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">當你結束了</span><span class=\"GramE\">一</span>次長休時，如果你和惡魔<span class=\"GramE\">志存在</span>於同一位面，則書中所困挑戰等級最高的生物可以嘗試附身你。你必須進行一次DC20<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">的魅力豁免。若豁免失敗，則你如同一具提線玩偶般被該生物附身。附身你的生物可以用一個動作釋放你，並在最近的一處未佔據空間出現。若豁免成功，則嘗試附身你的邪魔在未來</span>7<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">天內都不能再次嘗試附身你。</span><br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">在</span><span class=\"GramE\">這本魔典被</span>發現時，已經有了[[/r 1d4]]<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">張書頁被佔據，一般是各種惡魔。</span><br /><em><strong>破壞惡魔志。</strong></em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">要摧毀這本書，必須有六位不同的惡魔領主分別撕下書的一頁。如果這種情況發生，書頁會在</span>24<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">小時內恢復。在這段時間過去之前，任何打開書的人都會被傳送到一處隱藏在書中的新生深淵層級。在這致命、的半智慧領域中心，有一件遺失許久的神器，弗拉茲</span>-<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">厄魯之杖。如果法杖被帶離這處口袋位面，</span><span class=\"GramE\">魔典會</span>立刻變成一本<em>《反序古典Tome of </em><span class=\"SpellE\"><em>Zyx</em></span><em>》</em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">普通而老舊的複製品，這本書是創造惡魔志的基底。法杖一旦出現，惡魔領主弗拉茲</span>-<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">厄魯會立刻知道這件事。</span></p></div>",
